      <p>阅读完整文章：<a href="https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/technology/ai/nano-banana-2/">https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/technology/ai/nano-banana-2/</a></p>
    `,
    contentEn: `
      <p>Google DeepMind today released <strong>Nano Banana 2</strong> (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image), the latest generation of image generation model following last year's viral Nano Banana sensation. This model combines the advanced features of Nano Banana Pro with the lightning speed of Gemini Flash, enabling users to achieve rapid edits and iteration while maintaining professional-grade quality.</p>
      
      <h2>Fusion of Speed and Intelligence</h2>
      <p>Nano Banana 2 brings Gemini Flash's high-speed intelligence to visual generation, making rapid edits and iteration possible. It makes once-exclusive Pro features accessible to a wider audience:</p>
      
