      <ul>
        <li>生成速度：51 tokens/秒</li>
        <li>首 token 延迟：1.5 秒</li>
        <li>内存占用：17.99 GB（基础）+ 3-4 GB/每倍上下文</li>
        <li>48K 上下文总内存：约 21 GB</li>
        <li>最大 256K 上下文：约 37.5 GB</li>
      </ul>

      <p>原文：<a href="https://ai.georgeliu.com/p/running-google-gemma-4-locally-with">https://ai.georgeliu.com/p/running-google-gemma-4-locally-with</a></p>
    `,
    contentEn: `
      <p>Advantages of running LLMs locally: zero API costs, data never leaves your machine, always available. Google Gemma 4's MoE architecture makes it ideal for local deployment.</p>

      <h2>Why Gemma 4 26B-A4B</h2>
      <p>The Mixture-of-Experts architecture is key: 128 experts + 1 shared expert, but only 8 experts (3.8B parameters) activate per token. Inference cost comparable to a 4B dense model, but quality far exceeds that class.</p>

      <h3>Performance Comparison</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Model</th><th>MMLU Pro</th><th>AIME 2026</th><th>Total Params</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Gemma 4 26B-A4B</td><td>82.6%</td><td>88.3%</td><td>26B</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Gemma 4 31B Dense</td><td>85.2%</td><td>89.2%</td><td>31B</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Qwen 3.5 397B-A17B</td><td>-</td><td>~1450 Elo</td><td>397B</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Kimi-K2.5</td><td>-</td><td>~1457 Elo</td><td>1000B+</td></tr>
      </table>

      <p>26B-A4B achieves near 400B+ model Elo scores with only 26B total parameters, dramatically reducing memory requirements.</p>

      <h2>LM Studio 0.4.0 New Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>llmster daemon</strong> — Background inference service without desktop app</li>
        <li><strong>lms CLI</strong> — Full command-line interface</li>
        <li><strong>Parallel request processing</strong> — Continuous batching instead of sequential queuing</li>
        <li><strong>Stateful REST API</strong> — /v1/chat endpoint maintains conversation history</li>
        <li><strong>MCP integration</strong> — Local Model Context Protocol support</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Quick Start</h2>
      <pre><code># Install lms CLI
curl -fsSL https://lmstudio.ai/install.sh | bash

# Start daemon
lms daemon up

# Download Gemma 4 26B
lms get google/gemma-4-26b-a4b

# Chat with stats
lms chat google/gemma-4-26b-a4b --stats</code></pre>

      <h3>Real-world Performance (M4 Pro 48GB)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Generation speed: 51 tokens/sec</li>
        <li>Time to first token: 1.5 sec</li>
        <li>Memory: 17.99 GB (base) + 3-4 GB per context doubling</li>
        <li>48K context total: ~21 GB</li>
        <li>Max 256K context: ~37.5 GB</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Source: <a href="https://ai.georgeliu.com/p/running-google-gemma-4-locally-with">https://ai.georgeliu.com/p/running-google-gemma-4-locally-with</a></p>
    `,
    tags: ['Google', 'Gemma', 'Local-AI', 'LM-Studio', 'Developer-Tools'],
    source: 'George Liu'
  },
